a variational principle for convection of heat ..Aagrawal, h.c..Bj. math. and mech. v.9, no. 6, 1960 ..Wa variational principle for convection of heat .authors extend variational principle of biot to various cases of heattransfer due to forced convection . numerical results are given forone-dimensional problems of fluid flowing between parallel walls withuniform or parabolic velocity profiles . agreement with exact solutionsis excellent .